title: Athletics at the 2015 Pan American Games – Women's high jump
text:
The women's <a href="high%20jump">high jump</a> competition of the <a href="Track%20and%20field">athletics</a> events at the <a href="2015%20Pan%20American%20Games">2015 Pan American Games</a> took place on July 22 at the <a href="CIBC%20Pan%20Am%20and%20Parapan%20Am%20Athletics%20Stadium">CIBC Pan Am and Parapan Am Athletics Stadium</a>. The <a href="Athletics%20at%20the%202011%20Pan%20American%20Games%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20high%20jump">defending</a> <a href="Pan%20American%20Games">Pan American Games</a> champion is <a href="Lesyani%20Mayor">Lesyani Mayor</a> of <a href="Cuba">Cuba</a>.

Qualification.
Each <a href="National%20Olympic%20Committee">National Olympic Committee</a> (NOC) was able to enter up to two entrants providing they had met the minimum standard (1.78) in the qualifying period (January 1, 2014 to June 28, 2015).
Results.
All results shown are in meters.
